<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="broadcast-v">broadcast <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'brɔːdkɑːst/    美 /'brɔːdkæst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi广播；播送：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The concert was <strong>broadcast live</strong> and attracted the largest audience in the history.
演唱会现场直播，并吸引了有史以来最多的观众。</p><footer>2019 浙江改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
